Terminals unused in grammar

   ERR


Grammar

    0 $accept: program $end

    1 program: declaration_list init_block

    2 init_block: INIT compound_statement

    3 declaration_list: declaration_list declaration
    4                 | %empty

    5 declaration: var_declaration
    6            | func_declaration

    7 var_declaration: type_specifier ID SCOL
    8                | type_specifier ID LSBR INTCONST RSBR SCOL

    9 type_specifier: INT
   10               | FLOAT
   11               | VOID

   12 func_declaration: type_specifier ID LPBR params RPBR compound_statement

   13 params: param_list
   14       | %empty

   15 param_list: param_list COMMA param
   16           | param

   17 param: type_specifier ID
   18      | type_specifier ID LSBR RSBR

   19 compound_statement: LFBR local_declarations statement_list RFBR

   20 local_declarations: local_declarations var_declaration
   21                   | %empty

   22 statement_list: statement_list statement
   23               | %empty

   24 statement: expression_statement
   25          | compound_statement
   26          | selection_statement
   27          | iteration_statement
   28          | break_statement
   29          | return_statement

   30 expression_statement: expression SCOL
   31                     | SCOL

   32 selection_statement: simple_selection
   33                    | simple_selection ELSE compound_statement

   34 simple_selection: IF LPBR expression RPBR compound_statement
   35                 | simple_selection ELSE IF LPBR expression RPBR compound_statement

   36 iteration_statement: LOOP LPBR expression RPBR statement

   37 break_statement: BREAK SCOL

   38 return_statement: RETURN SCOL
   39                 | RETURN expression SCOL

   40 expression: var ASSGN expression
   41           | simple_expression

   42 var: ID
   43    | ID LSBR expression RSBR

   44 simple_expression: additive_expression relop additive_expression
   45                  | additive_expression

   46 relop: LES
   47      | LEQ
   48      | GRE
   49      | GEQ
   50      | EQL
   51      | NEQ

   52 additive_expression: additive_expression addop term
   53                    | term

   54 addop: ADD
   55      | SUB

   56 term: term mulop factor
   57     | factor

   58 mulop: MUL
   59      | DIV

   60 factor: LPBR expression RPBR
   61       | var
   62       | func_call
   63       | INTCONST
   64       | FLOATCONST

   65 func_call: ID LPBR args RPBR

   66 args: arg_list
   67     | %empty

   68 arg_list: arg_list COMMA expression
   69         | expression


